OL,3,CMan admits mocking stadium disaster
OL,4,Cand racist abuse at Merseyside derby
OL,6,FA football fan has pleaded guilty to
OL,7,Fmocking a crowd disaster and shouting
OL,8,Fracist abuse at a Merseyside derby
OL,9,Fmatch.
OL,11,FJoel Barwise, 26, made pushing
OL,12,Fgestures towards during the game
OL,13,Fagainst at Anfield on 21 October last
OL,14,Fyear, the Crown Prosecution Service
OL,15,F(CPS) said.
OL,17,FHe was also spotted by a match steward
OL,18,Fshouting racist abuse when Liverpool
OL,19,Fplayer Mohamed Salah's name was
OL,20,Fannounced in the stadium.
