OL,6,FThe gestures were made to taunt the
OL,7,Fhome fans about the Heysel stadium
OL,8,Fdisaster, when 39 Juventus fans died
OL,9,Fin a crush before the club's European
OL,10,FCup final against Liverpool in May
OL,11,F1985.
OL,13,FThe incidents were reported and
OL,14,Fidentified Barwise committing the
OL,15,Foffences from CCTV at the game, the
OL,16,FCPS said.
