OL,3,CMan admits mocking stadium disaster
OL,4,Cand racist abuse at Merseyside derby
OL,6,FBarwise, of Bentham Drive in
OL,7,FChildwall, Liverpool, was arrested and
OL,8,Finitially said it was a case of
OL,9,Fmistaken identity, before later
OL,10,Fadmitting he was responsible.
OL,12,FAsked why he had done it, he said:
OL,13,F"Because I'm an idiot."
OL,15,FHe pleaded guilty to using
OL,16,Fthreatening, abusive words or
OL,17,Fbehaviour likely to cause harassment,
OL,18,Falarm or distress at Sefton
OL,19,FMagistrates' Court on Tuesday, 13
OL,20,FFebruary.
