OL,3,CMan admits mocking stadium disaster
OL,4,Cand racist abuse at Merseyside derby
OL,6,FHe was fined #500 and received a
OL,7,Ffootball banning order for three
OL,8,Fyears, meaning he cannot attend
OL,9,Ffootball matches in the UK over that
OL,10,Ftime.
OL,12,FWhen international matches are being
OL,13,Fstaged abroad, Barwise must surrender
OL,14,Fhis passport.
OL,16,FHe also cannot go within a mile of any
OL,17,FEverton match, home or away, or within
OL,18,Fa mile of Liverpool Lime Street
OL,19,Fstation on matchdays, the CPS said.
