OL,3,CMan admits mocking stadium disaster
OL,4,Cand racist abuse at Merseyside derby
OL,6,F"For his disgraceful behaviour, he is
OL,7,Fnow banned from following his team or
OL,8,Fany other UK team for three years, has
OL,9,Fbeen fined and has a criminal record.
OL,11,F"The Crown Prosecution Service hopes
OL,12,Fthis sends out a message to all
OL,13,Ffootball spectators that the law
OL,14,Fapplies in a football ground as it
OL,15,Fdoes anywhere else and this sort of
OL,16,Fbehaviour is criminal."
